('cito studievaardigheden', NULL, 'cito studievaardigheden', 'Bekijk de kaartlegenda. Welk symbool staat voor een ziekenhuis?', '["Het huis-symbool 🏠","Het kruis-symbool ✚","Het boom-symbool 🌲","Het ster-symbool ★"]'::jsonb, 1, 'Op kaarten staat een rood kruis (✚) altijd voor een ziekenhuis of medische post.', '<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 260 120"><rect width="260" height="120" rx="8" fill="#0d1f3c"/><text x="130" y="14" font-size="10" font-weight="bold" fill="#64b5f6" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">🗺 Legenda</text><rect x="14" y="22" width="120" height="92" rx="6" fill="#162033" stroke="#334" stroke-width="1"/><text x="74" y="36" font-size="9" font-weight="bold" fill="#64b5f6" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Legenda</text><text x="22" y="52" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">🏠</text><text x="38" y="52" font-size="9" fill="#ccc" font-family="sans-serif">= Woonwijk</text><text x="22" y="68" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">🌲</text><text x="38" y="68" font-size="9" fill="#ccc" font-family="sans-serif">= Park</text><text x="22" y="84" font-size="13" fill="#f48fb1" font-weight="bold" font-family="sans-serif">✚</text><text x="38" y="84" font-size="9" fill="#ccc" font-family="sans-serif">= Ziekenhuis </text><text x="22" y="100" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">🏫</text><text x="38" y="100" font-size="9" fill="#ccc" font-family="sans-serif">= School</text><rect x="148" y="22" width="100" height="92" rx="6" fill="#162033" stroke="#334" stroke-width="1"/><text x="188" y="50" font-size="11" fill="#ccc" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">🏠</text><text x="215" y="65" font-size="11" fill="#69f0ae" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">✚</text><text x="165" y="80" font-size="11" fill="#ccc" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">🌲</text><text x="200" y="88" font-size="11" fill="#ccc" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">🏫</text><text x="175" y="100" font-size="11" fill="#69