('cito groep8-studievaardigheden', NULL, 'cito groep8-studievaardigheden', 'Bekijk de tijdlijn. Hoe oud was Anne Frank toen ze zich verstopte?', '["10 jaar","11 jaar","12 jaar","13 jaar"]'::jsonb, 3, 'Anne Frank werd geboren in 1929 en ging in 1942 onderduiken: 1942 − 1929 = 13 jaar.', '<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 280 90"><rect width="280" height="90" rx="8" fill="#0d1f3c"/><text x="140" y="14" font-size="10" font-weight="bold" fill="#64b5f6" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">📅 Tijdlijn Anne Frank</text><line x1="20" y1="50" x2="260" y2="50" stroke="#334" stroke-width="2"/><circle cx="40" cy="50" r="4" fill="#f59e0b"/><text x="40" y="40" font-size="8" fill="#ccc" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">1929</text><text x="40" y="66" font-size="7.5" fill="#ccc" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Geboren</text><circle cx="130" cy="50" r="5" fill="#ffd700" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="1.5"/><text x="130" y="40" font-size="8" fill="#ffd700" font-weight="bold" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">1942</text><text x="130" y="66" font-size="7.5" fill="#ccc" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Onderduiken </text><circle cx="200" cy="50" r="4" fill="#f48fb1"/><text x="200" y="40" font-size="8" fill="#f48fb1" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">1944</text><text x="200" y="66" font-size="7.5" fill="#f48fb1" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Gearresteerd</text><circle cx="250" cy="50" r="4" fill="#aaa"/><text x="250" y="40" font-size="8" fill="#aaa" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">1945</text><text x="250" y="66" font-size="7.5" fill="#aaa" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Overlijden</text><line x1="40" y1="50" x2="130" y2="50" stroke="#ffd700" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-dasharray="4,2"/><text x="85" y="30" font-size="8" fill="#ffd700" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">13 jaar</text></svg>', 'topic', 'negatieve-getallen', 0, FALSE, NULL),
('cito groep8-studievaardigheden', NULL, 'cito groep8-studievaardigheden', 'Bekijk de schooldagtijdlijn. Hoe lang duurt de ochtendpauze?', '["10 minuten","15 minuten","20 minuten","30 minuten"]'::jsonb, 1, 'De pauze duurt van 10:15 tot 10:30 — dat is 15 minuten.', '<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 280 95"><rect width="280" height="95" rx="8" fill="#0d1f3c"/><text x="140" y="14" font-size="10" font-weight="bold" fill="#64b5f6" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">🏫 Schooldag tijdlijn</text><line x1="15" y1="50" x2="265" y2="50" stroke="#334" stroke-width="2.5"/><rect x="15" y="43" width="95" height="14" rx="3" fill="#1e88e5" opacity="0.7"/><text x="62" y="72" font-size="7.5" fill="#64b5f6" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Les (8:30–10:15)</text><rect x="110" y="43" width="22" height="14" rx="3" fill="#445" opacity="0.9"/><text x="121" y="72" font-size="7.5" fill="#ccc" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Pauze </text><rect x="132" y="43" width="88" height="14" rx="3" fill="#1e88e5" opacity="0.7"/><text x="176" y="72" font-size="7.5" fill="#64b5f6" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Les (10:30–12:15)</text><rect x="220" y="43" width="45" height="14" rx="3" fill="#f59e0b" opacity="0.7"/><text x="242" y="72" font-size="7.5" fill="#f59e0b" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Lunch</text><text x="15" y="42" font-size="7" fill="#aaa" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">8:30</text><text x="110" y="42" font-size="7" fill="#ccc" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">10:15</text><text x="132" y="42" font-size="7" fill="#ccc" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">10:30</text><text x="220" y="42" font-size="7" fill="#aaa" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">12:15</text><line x1="110" y1="43" x2="132" y2="43" stroke="#69f0ae" stroke-width="1.5"/><text x="121" y="33" font-size="8" fill="#ccc" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">15 min</text></svg>', 'topic', 'krac