('cito groep8-studievaardigheden', NULL, 'cito groep8-studievaardigheden', 'Bekijk de technologietijdlijn. Welke uitvinding is het oudst?', '["Internet (1969)","Mobiele telefoon (1983)","Telefoon (1876)","Smartphone (2007)"]'::jsonb, 2, 'De telefoon werd uitgevonden in 1876 — dat is het vroegste jaartal op de tijdlijn.', '<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 280 90"><rect width="280" height="90" rx="8" fill="#0d1f3c"/><text x="140" y="14" font-size="10" font-weight="bold" fill="#64b5f6" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">💡 Tijdlijn technologie</text><line x1="15" y1="50" x2="265" y2="50" stroke="#334" stroke-width="2"/><circle cx="30" cy="50" r="6" fill="#ffd700" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="1.5"/><text x="30" y="40" font-size="7.5" fill="#ffd700" font-weight="bold" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">1876</text><text x="30" y="68" font-size="7" fill="#ccc" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">📞 Tel. </text><circle cx="110" cy="50" r="4" fill="#64b5f6"/><text x="110" y="40" font-size="7.5" fill="#64b5f6" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">1969</text><text x="110" y="68" font-size="7" fill="#64b5f6" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">🌐 Internet</text><circle cx="175" cy="50" r="4" fill="#64b5f6"/><text x="175" y="40" font-size="7.5" fill="#64b5f6" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">1983</text><text x="175" y="68" font-size="7" fill="#64b5f6" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">📱 Mobiel</text><circle cx="248" cy="50" r="4" fill="#64b5f6"/><text x="248" y="40" font-size="7.5" fill="#64b5f6" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">2007</text><text x="248" y="68" font-size="7" fill="#64b5f6" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">📲 Smart</text></svg>', 'topic', 'logaritmen', 0, FALSE, NULL),
('cito groep8-studievaardigheden', NULL, 'cito groep8-studievaardigheden', 'Bekijk de tijdlijn. Hoe oud was hij toen zijn eerste kind werd geboren?', '["25 jaar","28 jaar","30 jaar","32 jaar"]'::jsonb, 2, 'Geboren in 1975, eerste kind in 2005: 2005 − 1975 = 30 jaar.', '<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 280 90"><rect width="280" height="90" rx="8" fill="#0d1f3c"/><text x="140" y="14" font-size="10" font-weight="bold" fill="#64b5f6" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">📅 Tijdlijn leven</text><line x1="15" y1="50" x2="265" y2="50" stroke="#334" stroke-width="2"/><circle cx="30" cy="50" r="4" fill="#f59e0b"/><text x="30" y="40" font-size="7.5" fill="#ccc" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">1975</text><text x="30" y="68" font-size="7" fill="#ccc" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Geboren</text><circle cx="115" cy="50" r="4" fill="#aaa"/><text x="115" y="40" font-size="7.5" fill="#aaa" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">2002</text><text x="115" y="68" font-size="7" fill="#aaa" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Getrouwd</text><circle cx="195" cy="50" r="6" fill="#ffd700" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="1.5"/><text x="195" y="40" font-size="7.5" fill="#ffd700" font-weight="bold" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">2005</text><text x="195" y="68" font-size="7" fill="#ccc" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">1e kind </text><line x1="30" y1="50" x2="195" y2="50" stroke="#ffd700" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-dasharray="4,2" opacity="0.5"/><text x="112" y="30" font-size="8" fill="#ffd700" text-anchor="middle" font-weight="bold" font-family="sans-serif">30 jaar</text></svg>', 'topic', 'negatieve-getallen', 0, FALSE, NULL),
