('cito groep8-studievaardigheden', NULL, 'cito groep8-studievaardigheden', 'Bekijk de vluchtinformatie. Hoe lang duurt de vlucht?', '["1 uur 45 min","2 uur 15 min","2 uur 45 min","3 uur 15 min"]'::jsonb, 2, 'Vertrek 09:45, aankomst 12:30. Van 09:45 naar 12:30 is 2 uur en 45 minuten.', '<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 260 110"><rect width="260" height="110" rx="8" fill="#0d1f3c"/><text x="130" y="14" font-size="10" font-weight="bold" fill="#64b5f6" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">✈️ Vluchtinformatie</text><rect x="10" y="22" width="240" height="80" rx="6" fill="#162033" stroke="#334" stroke-width="1"/><text x="20" y="42" font-size="9" fill="#aaa" font-family="sans-serif">Vlucht:</text><text x="120" y="42" font-size="9" fill="#ccc" font-family="sans-serif">KL 1247</text><text x="20" y="58" font-size="9" fill="#aaa" font-family="sans-serif">Van:</text><text x="120" y="58" font-size="9" fill="#ccc" font-family="sans-serif">Amsterdam (AMS)</text><text x="20" y="72" font-size="9" fill="#aaa" font-family="sans-serif">Naar:</text><text x="120" y="72" font-size="9" fill="#ccc" font-family="sans-serif">Barcelona (BCN)</text><text x="20" y="86" font-size="9" fill="#aaa" font-family="sans-serif">Vertrek:</text><text x="120" y="86" font-size="9" fill="#64b5f6" font-weight="bold" font-family="sans-serif">09:45</text><text x="20" y="98" font-size="9" fill="#aaa" font-family="sans-serif">Aankomst:</text><text x="120" y="98" font-size="9" fill="#64b5f6" font-weight="bold" font-family="sans-serif">12:30</text></svg>', 'topic', 'krachten-natuurkunde', 4, FALSE, NULL),
('cito groep8-studievaardigheden', NULL, 'cito groep8-studievaardigheden', 'Bekijk het keuze-schema (beslisboom). Hoeveel verschillende outfits zijn er mogelijk?', '["2 outfits","3 outfits","4 outfits","6 outfits"]'::jsonb, 2, '2 weertypes (zonnig/regenachtig) × 2 temperaturen (warm/koud) = 4 mogelijke outfits.', '<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 260 120"><rect width="260" height="120" rx="8" fill="#0d1f3c"/><text x="130" y="14" font-size="10" font-weight="bold" fill="#64b5f6" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">👗 Keuze-schema outfit</text><rect x="100" y="22" width="60" height="18" rx="4" fill="#1a3a5c" stroke="#64b5f6" stroke-width="1"/><text x="130" y="35" font-size="8.5" fill="#64b5f6" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Weer?</text><line x1="115" y1="40" x2="70" y2="58" stroke="#aaa" stroke-width="1.5"/><line x1="145" y1="40" x2="190" y2="58" stroke="#aaa" stroke-width="1.5"/><rect x="40" y="58" width="60" height="16" rx="4" fill="#1a2744" stroke="#f59e0b" stroke-width="1"/><text x="70" y="70" font-size="8" fill="#f59e0b" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">☀️ Zonnig</text><rect x="160" y="58" width="60" height="16" rx="4" fill="#1a2744" stroke="#64b5f6" stroke-width="1"/><text x="190" y="70" font-size="8" fill="#64b5f6" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">🌧 Regenachtig</text><line x1="55" y1="74" x2="35" y2="90" stroke="#aaa" stroke-width="1.5"/><line x1="85" y1="74" x2="105" y2="90" stroke="#aaa" stroke-width="1.5"/><line x1="175" y1="74" x2="155" y2="90" stroke="#aaa" stroke-width="1.5"/><line x1="205" y1="74" x2="225" y2="90" stroke="#aaa" stroke-width="1.5"/><rect x="18" y="90" width="34" height="14" rx="3" fill="#334" opacity="0.8"/><text x="35" y="101" font-size="7" fill="#ccc" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Warm</text><rect x="88" y="90" width="34" height="14" rx="3" fill="#334" opacity="0.8"/><text x="105" y="101" font-size="7" fill="#ccc" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-